casebody.data:
No. 10-7875. Marlin E. Jones, Petitioner v. Midstates Development, Inc., et al. 562 U.S. 1197, 131 S. Ct. 1054,

178 L. Ed. 2d 860,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 990. January 24, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Nebraska dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
